<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">特别的日子</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">特别的策划给</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">特别的B230503班的同学</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">留下特别的印象</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713367531157050397.png" title="1713367531157050397.png" alt="image.png" width="393" height="372" style="width: 393px; height: 372px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">主持人组织大家参与游戏</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">现场随机分成两组</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">大家全身心投入</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">争取让自己所在的队伍赢得胜利</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">还有一些同学为</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">大家带来个人才艺秀</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">让现场的气氛逐渐热烈</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">教室中充满了</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">老师们和同学们的欢声笑语</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713367558851072441.png" title="1713367558851072441.png" alt="image.png" width="470" height="252" style="width: 470px; height: 252px;"/></p>